<Author>AussieUmsa
<Content>Great place to stay This hotel is in a good location with a train sation across the road. Access into the city centre is 2 stops away. The hotel is clean. In particular the room and bathroom were well presented and clean, as well as providing all the necessary facilities like hair dryer etc. The spread for breakfast in the morning was much better than we expected (although that cost an extra 11 Euros each) and offered a wide variety of stuff. We found that if we had a sumptuous breakfast, some snacks through the day kept us going till dinner. There are a couple of restaurants near the hotel but they are a bit pricey. The receptionists spoke good english and were very helpful. All the staff we dealt with were very pleasant. We would stay here again. 
